  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要给这个引擎的核心类图定个结构。最顶层应该是Project，它下面要挂两个东西：一个是Scenes，一个是ProjectSettings。Scenes是场景列表，ProjectSettings存全局配置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Project",
        "Scenes",
        "ProjectSettings"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Project和Scenes、ProjectSettings都是组合关系对吧？就是Project销毁了它们也跟着销毁的那种强拥有关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Project",
        "Scenes",
        "ProjectSettings"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，组合关系。然后Scenes下面有Nodes，这是场景里的节点树。Nodes这块比较复杂，节点之间要有父子层级，也要有相邻引用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scenes",
        "Nodes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我理一下，Nodes自己跟自己有三种关系：组合表示父子挂载、聚合表示松散引用、还有普通关联表示同级或邻居引用？另外节点自引用画成环状结构？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Nodes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这个意思。还有，每个Node要挂三个东西：Properties存序列化属性，Resources存引用的外部资源，Scripts存绑定的脚本组件。这三个都是组合关系，节点没了它们也没意义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Nodes",
        "Properties",
        "Resources",
        "Scripts"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把主干画出来：Project组合持有Scenes和ProjectSettings，Scenes组合持有Nodes，Nodes自身有组合、聚合、关联三种自引用，然后Nodes再组合持有Properties、Resources、Scripts。这样结构就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Project",
        "Scenes",
        "ProjectSettings",
        "Nodes",
        "Properties",
        "Resources",
        "Scripts"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Nodes和Scripts的关系我刚才说错了。Scripts应该是组件形式挂在Node上，但销毁Node时Scripts确实要跟着销毁，所以组合是对的。不过你刚才说的\"聚合\"自引用我想再确认下——那个其实是运行时动态添加的子节点，用组合更合适，聚合那个先去掉吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Nodes",
        "Scripts"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我核对一下：Nodes的自引用保留三种——组合（父子挂载）、聚合（先留着？）、普通关联（邻居）。还是按你最初说的保留聚合，只是确认下用途？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Nodes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "保留吧，聚合给那种临时挂载、生命周期不完全同步的子节点用，比如运行时动态创建的特效节点。三种自引用都有场景，就这样定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Nodes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "最终结构确认：Project组合Scenes和ProjectSettings；Scenes组合Nodes；Nodes有组合、聚合、关联三种自引用；Nodes再组合Properties、Resources、Scripts。图我画好了。",
